1%BB%A9ng-II-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-wkCXUydbKG3TixWOKpwyFg">Mạn hứng (II) kỳ 2 - 漫興其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Tr%C3%A3i/author-NlHfXoUXzue8FcsdIodRLQ">Nguyễn Trãi</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%E1%BB%AFu-Th%C4%83ng/T%E1%BA%B7ng-H%C3%A0-N%E1%BB%99i-%C4%90%E1%BB%93ng-C%E1%BB%95-t%E1%BB%AB/poem-pmIZkYDzHf7xQByfDxT-QA">Tặng Hà Nội Đồng Cổ từ - 贈河內銅鼓祠</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-H%E1%BB%AFu-Th%C4%83ng/author-o7Hf6CJEKu5UA5pXP2ZmbA">Nguyễn Hữu Thăng</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%C3%B9-Vi-Thi%E1%BB%81u-Ch%C3%A2u-ki%E1%BA%BFn-k%C3%BD/poem-7nKp78KQjaTsc028x6cDMg">Thù Vi Thiều Châu kiến ký - 酬韋韶州見寄</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%C3%AAn/Ti%E1%BB%85n-D%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-tri-nh%E1%BA%ADm-m%C3%A3n-t%C3%A2y-quy/poem-z1rxTbuEB8nBA-rKn5FpUg">Tiễn Dương đồng tri nhậm mãn tây quy - 餞楊同知任滿西歸</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BB%93-%C4%90%E1%BA%A1o-Nguy%C3%AAn/author-vNqjO3qn_lddcLSXVQdpGA">Bồ Đạo Nguyên</a>)<br>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/T%E1%BB%AD-V%C5%A9-Kim-L%C4%83ng-k%C3%BD-H%E1%BB%93ng-Ki%E1%BB%81u-thi-k%E1%BB%B3-3/poem-IGKb9rzRbqcx7BxIx0J_Bw">Tử Vũ Kim Lăng ký Hồng Kiều thi kỳ 3 - 子羽金陵寄紅橋詩其三</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%C3%A2m-H%E1%BB%93ng/author-og0yg1YWgltsRxS7PoXrcQ">Lâm Hồng</a>)<br></div>	</div>
